item.title: About
item.description: Kaptan İslam A. CYBER SECURITY RESEARCHER As a passionate high school student with a strong desire to pursue a career in cybersecurity, I have dedicated myself to working on web application security. Additionally, I improve my skills in both frontend and backend web development. With a keen interest in OSINT, I am expanding my knowledge and developing new skills in this area. I am passionate about sharing my knowledge and experience through blogging and I like to challenge with myself.
